Ilmishiren


1  Nadol ina kata pee elo ilo Kuoo le Ker abol obo le lelo mishiren oopishana, naning nabo e nena ng'uesi ong'uan naaishu ejo to ltoilo le ndarata, “Wou!” 
2   Nadol, naa ng'ura, embarta naibor, neeta ilo okedito enkawuo, o enkopiyia e nkitoo naishooki ninye, neipang alo.


3  Ore pee ebol ninye ilo mishire li aare, naning ina ng'ues e are naishu ejo, “Wou!” 
4   Neipang'u enkai barta nanyokie oleng, ore ilo okedito neishooki engolon meiwuang'ie eseriani aitung'uaa e nkop pee eyiang'a iltung'ana maate, neishooki ninye olalem sapuk.


5   Ore pee ebol olmishire le okuni, naning ina ng'ues e uni naishu ejo, “Wou!” Ng'ura, nadol nanu, embarta narok, ore ilo okedito neeta entemet te nkaina enye. 
6  Naning entoki naaijo oltoilo te mpolos e nana ng'uesi ong'uan naaishu ejo, “Emborei e mpilbil e nkano te mpesai nabo, o mboreitin uni o shairi te dinari. Kake mintarruoo eilata o enaisho oo sabibu.”


7  Ore pee ebol ninye olmishire li oong'uan, naning oltoilo le ina ng'ues e ong'uan naishu ejo, “Wou!” 
8   Nadol nanu, naa ng'ura embarta pus, ore enkarna e ilo okedito naa keji Keeya, neirukurukore ninye Enemeneng'a. Neishooki ninye engolon meitoria ematua e ong'uan e nkop, peyie ear metuata to lalem o to lameyu o too lmeitai o too ng'uesi e ntim naatii enkop.


9  Ore ebol ninye olmishire le imiet nadol ti abori olperere lo lasar iltauja le lelo apa ootaaraki te nkaraki ororei le Enkai o te nchakenisho naitayutuo. 
10  Neishir aajo to ltoilo sapuk, “Iyie Olaitoriani Kitok, Oyanyiti nesipa, kanu akenya inguana intalaku osarge lang te lelo ootii enkop?” 
11  Neishori pooki te lelo olkila oibor, nejokini meyeng'iyeng'ata te nkiti kata, o metaba anaa neiputayu esiana e lelo ooisiaaishote te nebo ninche leton eitokini aar anaa apa ninche maate.


12   Ore pee ebol olmishire le ile, naing'orisho naa ng'ura, nadol etii enkikirikirata sapuk enkop, neroku enkolong netiu anaa olkila orok, neibelekenya olapa olulung'a netiu anaa osarge. 
13   Nesulunye lakir to loing'ang'e nesulakino enkop anaa lng'abolo oorrarrunye ilng'anayio te nkata enkirobi eyukito olkutati. 
14   Neng'ishari oloing'ang'e anaa olpiyayati otununukoki. Neiwuang'ieki pooki doinyo, o pooki lemankale aaitung'uaa ewueji enye. 
15   Ore laiguanak le na kop, o ltung'ana kituaak, o larikok loo njorin, o lkarsisi o loogol, o pooki ng'ae, orrindik aashu ololakuno. Neisudori too nkapuniaa o too isoito loo ldoinyo, 
16   neipot nejoki ildoinyo o soito, “Entusulakinoto iyiook, nisudoo iyiook too nkonyek e ilo otonita to lorika le nkitoo, o te ngoro e ilo Kuoo le Ker. 
17   Amu etabawua ina olong kitok e ngoro enye, naa ae ng'ae oidim aitasho te dukuya ninye?”

